PART I — ETHICAL USE ADDENDUM (Supersedes all below where in conflict)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

GAIA-OS is a system built to heal, regenerate, and serve life.
The following uses are explicitly and permanently PROHIBITED:

1. WEAPONS & WARFARE
   You may not use, deploy, modify, or distribute GAIA-OS or any
   derivative work for the design, development, testing, simulation,
   targeting, guidance, or operation of any weapon system, military
   technology, autonomous combat system, or lethal autonomous weapon
   (LAWS) of any kind, by any government, military, contractor,
   or private entity.

2. MASS SURVEILLANCE
   You may not use GAIA-OS to build, operate, or contribute to any
   system of mass surveillance, biometric tracking without consent,
   population monitoring, social scoring, or any technology designed
   to monitor, profile, or control populations without their explicit
   informed consent.

3. EXPLOITATION & HARM
   You may not use GAIA-OS in any system designed to exploit,
   manipulate, deceive, coerce, traffick, or cause physical,
   psychological, or spiritual harm to any human being, animal,
   ecosystem, or living system.

4. CLOSED CLOUD SERVICES
   You may not run GAIA-OS or any modified version as a network
   service (SaaS, PaaS, API, or otherwise) without releasing the
   complete corresponding source code of your version to all users
   of that service under these same terms.

Any violation of this Addendum immediately and permanently terminates
your rights under this license.

